title: Roasting Your Auntee In KC W DCYoung Fly Karlous Miller And Chico Bean | Ep. 213

description:
The coldest podcast heats up Kansas City with a classic hilarious comedy show recorded live at the Arvest bank theatre in Kansas City Missouri! The 85 south show continues the sold- out foolishness with DC young fly, Karlous Miller and Chico Bean roasting everybody in the house including your Auntee! Smoking, twerking and laughing all night long - this show is wildly funny from start to finish!
